        "passive": "*Activates the Entrance Animation when there is another\n\"Majin Buu Saga\" Category ally on the team upon the\ncharacter's entry*\n- Damage reduction rate 90% ⬆️\n- Damage reduction rate 15% ⬇️ for every turn passed\n(no more than -90%)\n- Chance of performing a critical hit 50% ⬆️ for 5 turn(s)\n*Basic effect(s)*\n- Ki +2\n- ATK & DEF 150% ⬆️\n- Medium chance of performing a critical hit\n- Launches an additional attack that has a great chance of\nbecoming a Super Attack\n*When attacking with 12 or more Ki*\n- ATK & DEF 150% ⬆️\n*For every Super Attack performed*\n- Damage reduction rate 5% ⬆️ (up to 30%)\n*When there is another \"Majin Buu Saga\" Category ally\nattacking in the same turn*\n- DEF 100% ⬆️ and guards all attacks as the 1st attacker in a\nturn\n- ATK 100% ⬆️ and launches an additional Super Attack as the\n2nd or 3rd attacker in a turn\n*When receiving a Ki Blast Super Attack*\n- High chance of nullifying it and countering with tremendous\npower",
        "activeSkill": "✨ FULL POWER KAMEHAMEHA ✨\nCondition: Can be activated when there is another \"Majin Buu Saga\" Category ally attacking in the same turn starting from the 4th turn from the start of battle (once only).\nEffet: Massively raises ATK temporarily, \ncauses ultimate damage to enemy and, \nwithin the turn activated, \nall attacks become critical hits",
